    rec("RLN-P1-C01-Entry1-6-1", "With $\\varphi(q)$, $\\psi(q)$, and $f(-q)$ as in (1.1.6)–(1.1.8): (i) $\\dfrac{f^3(-q)}{f^3(-q^5)}=\\dfrac{\\psi(q)}{\\psi(q^5)}\\cdot\\dfrac{\\psi^2(q)-5q\\psi^2(q^5)}{\\psi^2(q)-q\\psi^2(q^5)}$; (ii) $\\dfrac{f^6(-q^2)}{f^6(-q^{10})}=\\dfrac{\\psi^4(q)}{\\psi^4(q^5)}\\cdot\\dfrac{\\psi^2(q)-5q\\psi^2(q^5)}{\\psi^2(q)-q\\psi^2(q^5)}$; (iii) $\\dfrac{f^3(-q^2)}{q f^3(-q^{10})}=\\dfrac{\\varphi(q)}{\\varphi(q^5)}\\cdot\\dfrac{5\\varphi^2(q^5)-\\varphi^2(q)}{\\varphi^2(q)-\\varphi^2(q^5)}$; (iv) $\\dfrac{f^6(-q)}{q f^6(-q^5)}=\\dfrac{\\varphi^4(-q)}{\\varphi^4(-q^5)}\\cdot\\dfrac{5\\varphi^2(-q^5)-\\varphi^2(-q)}{\\varphi^2(-q^5)-\\varphi^2(-q)}$."),
